[Transcriber's note: Spelling used is exactly as in the original,
including typographic errors (e.g. _umbrella_ for _umbella_). This
UTF8 text contains accented Latin characters and accented Greek
characters. Also various astronomical symbols, the explanation of
which will be found in Linnaeus' _Species Plantarum_. Although the
title page bears the date 1788, the work was issued in parts
beginning with the text and first plates in 1789; further sets of
plates were issued up to 1792; plates 35 to 43 were never published.
At some time early in the 19th century the work was re-issued, still
with date 1788, but with type reset to 20 pages and lacking the
astronomical symbols.]

